i>\n<li>[i18n] Updated translation file</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2>Update</h2>\n<p>The update is available via your dashboards regular update process for installations with a valid license.</p>\n<h2>Paradise lost</h2>\n<p>Today in Sipalay, in the Philippines, I came across this tourism office. Perhaps useful to go there some time. But at the same time I wondered why it was there at all. This town has no tourism to speak of <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72x72/1f609.png" alt="&#x1f609;" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> </p>\n<p><a href="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-11278 lightbox-1"><img src="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office.jpg" alt="sipalay-tourism-office" width="960" height="960" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11278" srcset="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office-100x100.jpg 100w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office-300x300.jpg 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office-768x768.jpg 768w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office-200x200.jpg 200w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office-260x260.jpg 260w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office-380x380.jpg 380w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sipalay-tourism-office.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:3:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Payment gateway plugins updated";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s: