solete field in the database has been removed, old adverts will be migrated over to the &#8220;new&#8221; system which was introduce almost 2 years ago. changes Phoney hamburgers When you [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"Arnan";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2283:"<p><a href="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512.png" rel="lightbox-0"><img src="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-100x100.png" alt="logo-512x512" width="100" height="100" class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-699" srcset="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-100x100.png 100w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-300x300.png 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-150x150.png 150w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-200x200.png 200w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-450x450.png 450w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512-90x90.png 90w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/logo-512x512.png 512w" sizes="(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px" /></a>A small update with a few tweaks to the overall dashboard. AdRotate 3.14.1 is tested to work on WordPress 4.4 with no known issues. An obsolete field in the database has been removed, old adverts will be migrated over to the &#8220;new&#8221; system which was introduce almost 2 years ago.</p>\n<h2>changes</h2>\n<div class="shortcode-unorderedlist arrow">\n<ul>\n<li>[change] Few dashboard updates, better wording and such</li>\n<li>[change] Removed obsolete &#8216;link&#8217; column from database</li>\n<li>[i18n] Updated translation strings</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2>Phoney hamburgers</h2>\n<p>When you order a hamburger you expect a round pattie. Some lettuce, tomato and a circular piece of ground beef.</p>\n<p>Not this &#8211;<br />\n<a href="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/filipino-hamburger.jpg" rel="lightbox-1"><img src="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/filipino-hamburger-1024x768.jpg" alt="filipino-hamburger" width="1024" height="768" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-9626" srcset="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/filipino-hamburger-300x225.jpg 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/filipino-hamburger-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/filipino-hamburger.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>\n<p>Even though the taste was ok, it&#8217;s not a hamburger.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:3:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:38:"Automatic update bug – Fixed, but…";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"https://ajdg.solutions/2015/12/05/automatic-update-bug-fixed-but/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 04 Dec 2015 19:08:04 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Plugins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"adrotate";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b: